{"parentUuid":"a7ab7d78-1327-4ad7-8be8-5dcf34e1175f","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"e3c09006-364b-4553-aca3-8e2f57b0bf93","version":"2.1.42","gitBranch":"HEAD","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"Groq API 网络不通（需要代理）,怎么解决"},"uuid":"564fa8e5-4a39-4e0a-93df-6c6d3adf8e50","timestamp":"2026-02-15T14:32:38.253Z","thinkingMetadata":{"maxThinkingTokens":31999},"todos":[],"permissionMode":"default"}
{"parentUuid":"564fa8e5-4a39-4e0a-93df-6c6d3adf8e50","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"e3c09006-364b-4553-aca3-8e2f57b0bf93","version":"2.1.42","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"content":[{"text":"Groq API 需要代理才能访问，有几种常见解决方案：\n\n**方案1：设置环境变量代理**\n\n在 bash 中设置：\n```bash\nexport https_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:7890\nexport http_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:7890\n```\n\n把 `7890` 换成你本地代理的实际端口（Clash 默认 7890，V2Ray 默认 10809）。\n\n**方案2：在代码中设置代理（Python）**\n\n```python\nimport os\nos.environ[\"https_proxy\"] = \"http://127.0.0.1:7890\"\n```\n\n或者用 `httpx` 客户端时直接传 proxy：\n```python\nimport httpx\nclient = httpx.Client(proxy=\"http://127.0.0.1:7890\")\n```\n\n**方案3：如果用 Groq 的官方 SDK**\n\n```python\nfrom groq import Groq\nimport httpx\n\nclient = Groq(\n    http_client=httpx.Client(proxy=\"http://127.0.0.1:7890\")\n)\n```\n\n---\n\n你本地用的什么代理软件？我可以帮你确认端口号和具体配置。","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_20260215143240","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":1383,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":19274,"output_tokens":324,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"aea0877a-85ba-46c7-8919-859c016bc2d4","timestamp":"2026-02-15T14:32:46.610Z"}
